>>> Sorry, I just noticed you are assigning hdiv and vdiv directly to width and height, which looks wrong.
>>>
>>> It should be:
>>>
>>> src_c.width = src_y.width / cap->pix.info->hdiv;
>>> src_c.height = src_y.height / cap->pix.info->vdiv;
